metadata.name: Monkeypox - July 23rd, 2022

attributes.value: Monkeypox is now a global emergency, World Health Organization says

In this digital art piece, a monkey is shown with a large, red rash on its face. The monkey is surrounded by a group of people in hazmat suits, who are holding a sign that reads "Monkeypox is now a global emergency, World Health Organization says". The background is a dark, stormy sky, and the overall tone of the piece is one of alarm and concern.
